text: Sold 10% of my Spot $SOL here at 216. Still holding around 80%. Current plan is to take 60-70% out till 260 and leave the rest in case we get a noteworthy Sol Treasury Lead similar to Saylor or Tom Lee. 220 seems like resistence to me so offloading some here makes sense imo.
